title: #145 - We Actually Stormed Area 51
description: On this episode of the H3 Podcast we talk to Ethan's brother Sean who did some first hand gumshoe reporting at the Area 51 base camp this past weekend! We also talk about Hila's citizenship oath ceremony, Justin Trudeau's deep affection for offensive costumes, and cringey fathers using their pregnant wives for views!
